{"tid":1932281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"耿爽告訴美方所有選項都在中方桌面上","createTime":"2020-03-18T15:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T19:01:58.000Z","uid":109780,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"07a31b5cc36f48af9f15f867f5fa840f8697f949","tid":1932281,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:29:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>#外交部回應是否擔心美方進一步反制#</strong><br />\n今天，記者就中方是否擔心美方採取進一步反制措施提問，對此，外交部發言人耿爽表示，我們的立場很明確，我們敦促美國立即改弦更張、糾正錯誤，停止對中國媒體的政治打壓和無理的限制。如果美方一意孤行，錯上加錯，中方必將被迫採取進一步的反制措施。<br />\n耿爽強調，美方曾經說過，所有的選項都在桌面上。今天我也可以告訴美方，所有的選項也都在中方的桌面上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZymYX8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZymYX8.jpg&h=0b1a83c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PTSCxiv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPTSCxiv.jpg&h=c0a8bf34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNqTP5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNqTP5b.jpg&h=21209905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知連登仔嘅反應一定係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但係時候停止打飛機，Twitter要人啊</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8f269ac48ad51b6f62c25b038e58d5882184a31d","tid":1932281,"uid":21141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:31:19.000Z","msg":"又來耿爽模擬器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ebacb707f5e568f1944f887d641bc47ddd4567","tid":1932281,"uid":344379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:54:36.000Z","msg":"(有新料爆)有間藍扮黃 呃手足錢 發國難財賣黑心口罩既舖頭需要大家狙擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1928727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1928727</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8f802f96b5c29008039545643d4e0d2b59e81e94","tid":1932281,"uid":157138,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202